725240f-a.title: Queens: 35th Street - 20th Road
725240f-a.text:
35th Street (right, along cemetery and row of two family houses),
south from 2Oth Road (formerly Old Bowery Road; left foreground), and
21st Ave., showing at the corner the private cemetery of the Lawrence
family.
May 1926.
Eugene L. Ambruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

725099f-b.title: Queens: 20th Road - 35th Street
725099f-b.text:
20th Road, south side, west of 36th to 35th Streets, showing in
the foreground of this set of to views, the private cemetery of the
Lawrence family.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Ambruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3 A 4)
Views 3 and 4 are the same, showing the interior of the cemetery
grounds.
1927t
Arthur White.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
